# =============================================
# HyperPrism Reimagined — .gitignore
# =============================================
# Only track: Source code, CMakeLists.txt, JUCE submodule,
# ThirdParty deps, essential scripts, and project docs.

# ----- Claude / AI agent files -----
.claude/
.dvignore
.diversion/

# ----- macOS system files -----
.DS_Store
._*
.AppleDouble
.LSOverride
.Spotlight-V100
.Trashes
.TemporaryItems
.DocumentRevisions-V100
.fseventsd
.VolumeIcon.icns
.com.apple.timemachine.donotpresent
.AppleDB
.AppleDesktop
Network Trash Folder
Temporary Items
.apdisk
Icon?

