HyperPrismReimagined/build/
HyperPrismReimagined/build-*/
HyperPrismReimagined/build_test/
HyperPrismReimagined/build.log
HyperPrismReimagined/plugin_backups/
*.o
*.obj
*.a
*.lib
*.pdb
*.ilk
*.dll
*.so
*.dylib
temp_parser_*.cpp

